  "title": "Service Crew $2500 (F&B) North Indian Restaurant",
  "description": "<p><strong>Key Duties</strong></p><ul><li><p>Welcome guests with a friendly, attentive approach to ensure an enjoyable dining experience</p></li><li><p>Take customer orders accurately and deliver food and drinks promptly and professionally</p></li><li><p>Uphold high standards of cleanliness and sanitation across all dining and service areas</p></li><li><p>Complete daily setup and end-of-day procedures to ensure smooth operations</p></li><li><p>Work in coordination with kitchen staff and fellow team members to ensure efficient service flow</p></li><li><p>Be flexible with work schedules, including weekends and public holidays, as required</p></li></ul><p><strong>Skills and Experience</strong></p><ul><li><p>Strong interpersonal skills with a positive, team-oriented mindset</p></li><li><p>Previous experience in the food and beverage industry is an advantage</p></li><li><p>An enthusiasm for Indian cuisine and cultural traditions to better engage with guests</p></li></ul><p><strong>What We Offer</strong></p><ul><li><p>Competitive salary based on experience</p></li><li><p>Complimentary staff meals</p></li><li><p>Opportunities for professional development and career advancement</p></li><li><p>A friendly and encouraging workplace culture</p></li><li><p>Medical coverage<br /><br /><br />Interested candidates please call/ WhatsApp me at 88175405 or send your resume to aly@swiftsearchglobal.com</p><p>EA Personnel Name: Willie Goh<br />EA Personnel No: R2197853<br />EA License No: 18C9495</p></li></ul>",
